$

Upload to launchpad:
GIT-SUBREPO$ dput -f ppa:spog/ppa-xenial git-subrepo_0.4.1~1_source.changes

Add PPA containing 'git-subrepo' package:
$ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:spog/ppa-xenial
$ sudo apt-get update

Install 'git-subrepo' DEB using APT:
$ sudo apt update
$ apt search git-subrepo
$ sudo apt install git-subrepo
$ man git-subrepo
$ git subrepo ...

